<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFAF6A10F7EC953C1423BFF3" pageId="84" pageNumber="842" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFAF6A10F7EC953C1423BFF3" blockId="84.[2063,2657,794,1217]" pageId="84" pageNumber="842">
Since its description, status of 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFAF6A10F634953C1461B8B4" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1916" box="[2504,2657,869,902]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Histiotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="84" pageNumber="842" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="laephotis">H. laephotis</taxonomicName>
has been confusing. It has been previously considered a full species and later a subspecies of 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFAF6A10F7969582170DB8CE" baseAuthorityName="Philippi &amp; Landbeck" baseAuthorityYear="1861" box="[2154,2317,987,1020]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Histiotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="84" pageNumber="842" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="montanus">H. montanus</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFAF6A10F6B2958217E4B8CE" baseAuthorityName="Poeppig" baseAuthorityYear="1835" box="[2382,2532,987,1020]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Histiotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="84" pageNumber="842" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="macrotus">H. macrotus</taxonomicName>
. It is now considered a distinct species by most authors based on morphological and ecological evidence. It is frequently mistaken with 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFAF6A10F6029208164BBFA8" baseAuthorityName="Poeppig" baseAuthorityYear="1835" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Histiotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="84" pageNumber="842" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="macrotus">H. macrotus</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFAF6A10F76592D81745BFA8" baseAuthorityName="Philippi &amp; Landbeck" baseAuthorityYear="1861" box="[2201,2373,1153,1178]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Histiotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="84" pageNumber="842" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="montanus">H. montanus</taxonomicName>
, therefore, accurate data in literature are scarce. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
